# .trivyignore — Trivy IaC scan suppressions for terraform-aws-agentcore
#
# Each suppression documents WHY it is accepted for a reusable Terraform module.
# Callers can override these defaults and add their own controls.
# Review this file when upgrading the module's defaults.
#
# Format: <AVD-ID> [exp:<YYYY-MM-DD>] [<comment>]

# S3 — access logging
# Callers are responsible for configuring server-access logging on the source
# bucket.  Enabling it inside the module would require a second bucket and
# additional permissions that most callers will want to control themselves.
AVD-AWS-0089

# S3 / ECR — AWS-managed vs. customer-managed KMS encryption
# Both resources are encrypted at rest using AWS-managed keys (SSE-S3 / AES-256).
# Requiring a CMK would force callers to create and manage a KMS key, which is
# disproportionate for the agent-source zip bucket and ECR images.
# Callers that require CMK encryption can pass an existing bucket/repo via the
# BYO-role escape hatch and manage encryption outside this module.
AVD-AWS-0132
AVD-AWS-0011

# IAM — wildcard Bedrock resource in the inline policy
# The execution role grants bedrock:InvokeModel on "*" by default so the agent
# can call any foundation model.  Callers should narrow this using
# additional_iam_statements and attach_bedrock_fullaccess_policy = false.
# The README documents this pattern explicitly.
AVD-AWS-0057
AVD-AWS-0030

# CodeBuild — artifact / cache encryption
# This CodeBuild project produces no stored artifacts (the image is pushed
# directly to ECR).  The NO_ARTIFACTS setting means there is no artifact
# encryption surface.  The ECR push is encrypted in transit by TLS.
AVD-AWS-0019

# CodeBuild — privileged mode
# privileged_mode = true is required to run the Docker daemon inside the
# build container so it can execute `docker build` and `docker push`.
# There is no alternative for container image build pipelines.
AVD-AWS-0008

# ECR — mutable image tags
# The module defaults to MUTABLE to allow iterative development (e.g. a
# rolling `latest` tag).  Callers should set ecr_image_tag_mutability =
# "IMMUTABLE" in production.  The README and examples document this pattern.
AVD-AWS-0031
